//TEXT
<jaT0001>Right, I'll go to the laboratory once again.
<enT0001>Right, I'll go to the laboratory once again.

//TEXT
<jaT0002>Right, I'll go to the infirmary once again.
<enT0002>Right, I'll go to the infirmary once again.

//TEXT
<jaT0003>Right, I'll go to the infirmary.
<enT0003>Right, I'll go to the infirmary.

//TEXT
<jaT0004>Right, I'll go to the guest rooms once again.
<enT0004>Right, I'll go to the guest rooms once again.

//TEXT
<jaT0005>I set out, being careful not to make any noise.
<enT0005>I set out, being careful not to make any noise.

//TEXT
<jaT0006>......
<enT0006>......

//TEXT
<jaT0007>While I was heading to my destination I passed by the central hallway. Slowly, but steadily, the time limit on our emergency power was approaching. I have to hurry...
<enT0007>While I was heading to my destination I passed by the central hallway. Slowly, but steadily, the time limit on our emergency power was approaching. I have to hurry...

//TEXT
<jaT0008>Maybe my impatience was getting the best of me. Even though moving around in this wide area was the most dangerous thing to do, it seems like I lost my concentration.
<enT0008>Maybe my impatience was getting the best of me. Even though moving around in this wide area was the most dangerous thing to do, it seems like I lost my concentration.

//TEXT
<jaT0009>Suddenly, I sensed someone and spun around...
<enT0009>Suddenly, I sensed someone and spun around...

//TEXT
<jaT0010>But before I knew it, Yu was standing surprisingly close to me.
<enT0010>But before I knew it, Yu was standing surprisingly close to me.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0011>"Dammit!"
<enT0011>"Dammit!"

//TEXT
<jaT0012>I tried to run. If I returned fire in this vacant hallway, I would never win against her firepower. If I could just escape to the corner right in front of me...
<enT0012>I tried to run. If I returned fire in this vacant hallway, I would never win against her firepower. If I could just escape to the corner right in front of me...

//TEXT
<jaT0013>It was all too late. No, it was already too late the moment she caught me off guard.
<enT0013>It was all too late. No, it was already too late the moment she caught me off guard.

//TEXT
<jaT0014>By the time I took my first step, Yu had already set her sights.
<enT0014>By the time I took my first step, Yu had already set her sights.

//TEXT
<jaT0015>A thunderous roar. The barrage of merciless gunshots resounded through the hall and red sparks fell to the floor. One of those bullets hit my leg.
<enT0015>A thunderous roar. The barrage of merciless gunshots resounded through the hall and red sparks fell to the floor. One of those bullets hit my leg.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0016>"Gah!"
<enT0016>"Gah!"

//TEXT
<jaT0017>I pitched forward and landed on the floor.
<enT0017>I pitched forward and landed on the floor.

//TEXT
<jaT0018>I couldn't move my leg. The pain might go away in a few minutes, but a hardened soldier like her wasn't going to give me that time.
<enT0018>I couldn't move my leg. The pain might go away in a few minutes, but a hardened soldier like her wasn't going to give me that time.

//TEXT
<jaT0019>I wasn't going to just wait for my death so I took a gamble and tried to ready my gun, but...
<enT0019>I wasn't going to just wait for my death so I took a gamble and tried to ready my gun, but...

//TEXT
<jaT0020>She quickly crushed my hopes.
<enT0020>She quickly crushed my hopes.

//TEXT
<jaT0021>I couldn't move my leg. Still, I can't just lie here and wait for Yu's second attack. I desperately readied my gun and tried to aim for Yu.
<enT0021>I couldn't move my leg. Still, I can't just lie here and wait for Yu's second attack. I desperately readied my gun and tried to aim for Yu.

//TEXT
<jaT0022>However, she wouldn't give me that chance.
<enT0022>However, she wouldn't give me that chance.

//TEXT
<jaT0023>Yu's eyes were ice cold. She didn't approach me, she just rained down bullets. It was the most effective attack now that I couldn't move.
<enT0023>Yu's eyes were ice cold. She didn't approach me, she just rained down bullets. It was the most effective attack now that I couldn't move.

//TEXT
<jaT0024>In no time, the hallway was stained in red blood. After the finishing blow, she fired off another round, and my consciousness faded into darkness...
<enT0024>In no time, the hallway was stained in red blood. After the finishing blow, she fired off another round, and my consciousness faded into darkness...

//TEXT
<jaT0025>......
<enT0025>......

//TEXT
<jaT0026>...
<enT0026>...

